{"tid":2006462,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"呢幾年嚟我深切體會一樣野：切忌溫水煮蛙","createTime":"2020-05-07T19:20:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-02T03:35:11.000Z","uid":307619,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"62a20fbe2cd33f04f70d27725ba78a4d4b6de089","tid":2006462,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T19:20:46.000Z","msg":"見到好多人討論緊出定係唔出<br />\n討論緊邊個叫人送頭 邊個係鬼<br />\n其實過去發生咁多事<br />\n不論大家決定出定係唔出<br />\n我相信咁大個人自己識決定<br />\n亦都尊重每一個人嘅決定<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OGc985A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOGc985A.jpg&h=74332e6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個人愚見<br />\n所有問題唔係一朝一夕發生<br />\n每日嘅荒誕不停蔓延<br />\n反常變為日常<br />\n無論一四年嘅雨傘<br />\n抑或係去年發生嘅種種荒謬<br />\n說到底習慣荒謬比荒謬本身更要荒謬<br />\n<br />\n過去嘅日子我哋已經失去咗太多<br />\n好多事情已經無法挽回<br />\n而聽日更加係梓樂離開我哋嘅第六個月<br />\n<br />\n呢幾年嚟自己好深刻咁體會到一樣嘢<br />\n就係好多嘢都唔單只係一個結果 <br />\n更加係一個過程<br />\n香港人已經溫水煮蛙咗好多年<br />\n一直都係去到盡頭先識得叫救命<br />\n不過現實係始終有班裝睡的人根本點都叫唔醒<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">至於每一個手足<br />\n無論聽日點樣都好<br />\n希望大家一直都用自己嘅方式去關注國歌法<br />\n而唔係等問題嚟到嗰日先叫救命<br />\n一句到尾 同自己交代就可以</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申：尊重自由意志<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n4y5HqA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn4y5HqA.jpg&h=ba64e742&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4942ec12b4c9bef619aea14f26fb2505cca8ecb0","tid":2006462,"uid":308251,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T19:24:55.000Z","msg":"笑左張圖, 連登不嬲都鬼黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3f1eec3618c508b38e882dd40a363e44a3cec2a","tid":2006462,"uid":307619,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4942ec12b4c9bef619aea14f26fb2505cca8ecb0","tid":2006462,"uid":308251,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T19:24:55.000Z","msg":"笑左張圖, 連登不嬲都鬼黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T19:28:31.000Z","msg":"2020 仲嘈緊啲無聊野"},{"pid":"bfb476b3107406d4a2c074577d08caeb35d95084","tid":2006462,"uid":310817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T19:29:13.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4219daee6aeedd437f3f56d86d002be4fee098b5","tid":2006462,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bfb476b3107406d4a2c074577d08caeb35d95084","tid":2006462,"uid":310817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T19:29:13.000Z","msg":"push"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T19:32:12.000Z","msg":"理性post無人理"},{"pid":"bf896130af32fdf9aea2f2856f049a1e892b967a","tid":2006462,"uid":208011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T19:34:48.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7c631b771eaaa1f642513b1424bfadcda4b302a9","tid":2006462,"uid":162268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T19:58:13.000Z","msg":"尊重勇武<br />\n為冇執政意志嘅香港人附上鮮血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2588473f75b16aa60d98cb62df3980e518a71fd5","tid":2006462,"uid":15298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T20:00:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db43b86d855491fd24739ab1c9701b6ffe9b7d04","tid":2006462,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T20:08:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d2d5e155dd45c76cfe79b80f8149be30a5d7da8","tid":2006462,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c631b771eaaa1f642513b1424bfadcda4b302a9","tid":2006462,"uid":162268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T19:58:13.000Z"